snippet.title: InfiniteCorp: Cyberpunk Revolution - First Look Gameplay / (PC)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1252170/InfiniteCorp_Cyberpunk_Revolution/
You are an employee of a corporation dealing in goods distribution and logistics in the “megatower” – the place where all local citizens live. Join a world where the stakes are high, and morality is blurred.
